Program: The Forum
Title: Do You Know What You’re Eating?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0412930
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 20 Jul 2016
If you think of your favourite foods – chocolate, maybe, or samosas, or pizza – do you really know where all the ingredients came from? Bridget Kendall asks the food scientist Chris Elliott, the software designer Jérôme Malavoy and the food labelling expert Monique Raats. Photo: The food label on a box of brownies (Getty Images) Show less